---
import Button from "../../ui/Button.astro";
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568901346375-23c9450c58cd?w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop"
    alt=""
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
    loading="eager"
    decoding="async"
  />

  <!-- Dark overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/90 via-black/70 to-black/40"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_bottom_right,_rgba(230,57,70,0.25),transparent_60%)]"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 relative z-10 pt-24 lg:pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl leading-[0.9] tracking-wide text-white mb-6">
        EL POS QUE<br />
        TU <span class="text-yellow">RESTAURANTE</span><br />
        <span class="text-yellow">NECESITA</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl">
        Cobra más rápido, lleva tu inventario al día y ve cómo va tu negocio en cualquier
        momento. Un solo sistema para tu restaurante, donde quiera que estés.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <Button href="#demo" variant="primary">Probar demo gratis</Button>
        <Button href="#features" variant="outline">Ver funciones</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Subtle bottom fade -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-white to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
</section>
